## Requirements

- [pixi](https://pixi.sh) вЂ” environment and dependency manager
- [just](https://just.systems) вЂ” task runner

## Installation

```zsh
git clone https://github.com/{{ github_username }}/{{ project_name }}.git
cd {{ project_name }}
just setup
```

`just setup` installs all dependencies (including bioconda packages) and
activates git hooks. Run it once after cloning.

