## Development tasks

Run `just` with no arguments to list all available recipes.

| Command | What it does |
|---|---|
| `just setup` | Install dependencies + activate pre-commit hooks (run once after cloning) |
| `just test` | Run the test suite with pytest |
| `just lint` | Lint code with ruff |
| `just format` | Auto-format code with ruff |
| `just typecheck` | Run mypy type checks |
| `just check` | Run lint + typecheck + test in sequence |
| `just notebook` | Start Jupyter Lab in notebooks/ |
| `just clean` | Remove caches and build artifacts |

