## Updating this project from the template

This project was generated from
[copier-bioinfo-template](https://github.com/tracelail/copier-bioinfo-template).
When the template receives improvements, pull them into this project:

```zsh
# Preview what would change without applying
copier update --trust --pretend

# Apply the update
copier update --trust
```

Copier performs a three-way merge. If there are conflicts, `.rej` files are
created next to the conflicting files вЂ” resolve them manually, delete the
`.rej` files, then commit.

